title: [1508521049] Griddled Chicken with Chickpeas, Feta & Watermelon Salad | Gordon Ramsay
description:
Young Holly Ramsay steps into the kitchen to give Gordon a hand, along with a sleepy hound providing a distraction. Remember to griddle the thighs skin side down to keep them extra juicy. Healthy and delicious - give it a try yourself for a brilliant light dinner.

Subscribe for weekly cooking videos.
